@Pakundo
Only the location of the achievement files has changed, thus they can be restored.

Go to;
%USERPROFILE%My DocumentsUbisoftTom Clancy's Ghost Recon Future SoldierprofilesSkidrow

and move data2, data1 and data0 to

%USERPROFILE%My DocumentsUbisoftTom Clancy's Ghost Recon Future SoldierprofilesSkidrow{random number}

@RMJ113,
